web.feedback.thanks_for_helping_onetime_.text: Thanks for helping Onetime Secret improve. It means a lot.

web.feedback.weve_built_this_tool_to_hel.text: We've built this tool to help you share sensitive info securely, and your real-world experiences are crucial for focusing our efforts. It helps us figure out what to work on next and how to make the service better for everyone.

web.feedback.hey_there_thanks_for_stoppi.text: Hey there, thanks for stopping by our feedback page. Your input isn't just welcome - it's crucial.

web.feedback.a_note_from_delano_founder_.text: A note from Delano, founder of Onetime Secret
